{"type": "article", "id": 58608, "title": "微博头部账号发广告需审核备案，Supreme 被评为年度最强 Logo | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-11-23T04:50:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 17934, "name": "感恩节"}, {"id": 720, "name": "微博"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181123121928eipoBVtvISqxzAjb.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一看的 case</h3><p><a href=\"http:// https://m.weibo.cn/status/4309080879328291?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">上海爱马仕之家今年冬季橱窗主题为“玩家”，</a>与艺术家陆平原合作。冬季橱窗在现实和虚实的交错叙事中，打造成玩具之家，展现儿时回忆和场景。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122006TZWusdNbjOqkgyn0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.512334\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122008Ks3RJU94egujZVq2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.903010\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811231220098YU15lqQgtivLKX7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.637544\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122009iKNlxrC4ZDwuJUcb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.512334\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122010v0GInplfmgWeKysJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122011CXLahm1wq6zeZPTB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://app.fansiji.com/h5/wangyiheiw2/index.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>网易考拉推出了一支“猪脑引发网易特大危机公关” H5。</strong></a>主角“小美”在项目上线时因为自己的失误，在解决危机时又发生了啼笑不得的“事故”。这支 H5 最终是为了推广网易考拉在“黑五”的优惠活动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122032uRSNqg7EClBv0MtH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.865101\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZiwitDcVNiA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">西班牙彩票</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZiwitDcVNiA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">El Gordo de Navidad</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZiwitDcVNiA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">今年的圣诞广告</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZiwitDcVNiA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">蛮哲学的。</a></strong>主人公和《等待戈多》中的戈多一样日复一日重复着同样的生活方式，也包括天天买彩票中头等奖这件事。在他明白和其他人分享，才能感受到喜悦之前，他已经厌倦了重复的胜利了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=y0798vbuwq7\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bJ5dEtnQuP8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国电信运营商 Verzion 上线了感恩节广告</a>，</strong>短片展示了儿子在感恩节给父亲发信息时斟酌措辞的过程，观众也算是可以感同身受了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k0799oezj2y\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/creative-works/project/suprematika-busche-brand-identity\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">俄罗斯面包连锁店 Busche 推出了新的campaign</a>。</strong>它在圣彼得堡的街道上寻找适合的纹理和颜色，制作了一系列和街景相融合的海报。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122201Y7dqEomvWPw26as0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122200txcs4RX5Ay7mGbeh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.631250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122159A2NTIv4Lf6k1UtQO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.631250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122201l17UouNwqXVpa4nC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.631250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122203CWSrMbqG2nDmFRKh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.631250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1934183965/4309178077941867\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>微博管理员发布声明，</strong></a>头部账号发布广告须经审核备案，若违规或被禁言封号。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181123122359h4niM3boqTztGcj8.png\" data-ratio=\"0.976950\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/apple-lures-amv-creative-teams-silicon-valley/1519270\" rel=\"nofollow\">苹果从 AMV 挖走两支团队，他们将加入苹果的内部创意部门。</a></strong>Mike Crowe 和 Rob Messeter 将担任 iPhone 品牌的创意总监，Caio Giannella 和 Diego de Oliveira 将在今年年底离开 AMV 并成为苹果的创意副总监。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.bain.com/about/media-center/press-releases/2018/fall-luxury-goods-market-study/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">贝恩公司发布 “2018 年全球奢侈品行业研究报告”。</a></strong>报告显示，全球奢侈品市场销售额（包含奢侈品和奢侈体验）在汇率恒定的情况下增长 5 %，达到 1.2 万亿欧元。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.lyst.com/year-in-fashion-2018/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>全球时尚数据平台 Lyst 正式公布 2018 年时装街头圈多项趋势榜单，</strong></a>Supreme 被评为最强 Logo。</p><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/kJklWKtND7w\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash@rawpixelr</a></p>"}